data.description: If you are looking for panoramic west mountain views, look no further. This is a 10+. This newer build in the Enclave is nothing short of perfection. As you pass through the gated patio entrance, you'll be captivated by the seamless flow of the open floor plan, adorned with a gas fireplace and a gourmet kitchen suited to please any culinary enthusiast. As you cook or dine, indulge in the majestic mountain views that overlook the saltwater pool and spa equipped with cutting-edge wireless Hayward controls. The outdoor dining area, complete with ceiling fans and a gas barbecue hookup, invites you to savor al fresco delights, while the remote-control sunshades shield you from the afternoon sun. Enjoy raised garden beds, the bounty of fruit trees, or a spirited game of Bocce Ball. The primary bedroom is a sanctuary of indulgence, boasting a generous walk-in closet crafted by California Closets, a spa-like bath with a Toto wash-let, a spacious shower, and soaking tub. The generous guest room offers an ensuite bath and a walk-in closet, ensuring unparalleled comfort; and the third bedroom is thoughtfully fitted with built-in desks and a convenient Murphy bed, creating a versatile space that easily transforms to meet your needs. The rare 3-car garage is complete with ample storage shelving for your convenience. Embrace sustainability with a remote-controlled solar system (leased) and a Tesla backup battery (owned), showcasing your commitment to both style and eco-conscious living.
